title: Victor Vitale and His Tortuga Cigars...What's New?
itunes:title: Victor Vitale and His Tortuga Cigars...What's New?
description: Victor Vitale sits in for the whole show and discusses not only his lated cigar, the Tortuga Cedro, but we also smoke the first samples of the Tortuga Black Coyote. We heard some good news about the FDA and lots more on this week's episode of The Cigar Authority!
